description:
Solution templates for the .NET command-line interface and Visual Studio.
            Features:
            • Dependency Injection
            • Generic Host
            • StyleCop configuration file
            • .editorconfig file
            • Batch file that creates an initial migration and database using the selected provider.
			• appsettings.json
            • LICENSE file for the solution (Optional)
            • Logging
                - Generic Host
                - Serilog (Optional)
            • Data Access with Entity Framework Core
                - SQL Server Express LocalDB
                - SQL Server Express
                - Sqlite
            • AutoMapper (Optional)
            • FluentValidation (Optional)
            • MediatR (Optional)
